对于内核自带的模块, 如何进行单独编译:

以 ft1000 为例:
\starttyping
vi .config # enable ft1000 module: CONFIG_FT1000=m
make prepare # setup FT1000 as module
make modules_prepare
make SUBDIRS=drivers/staging/ft1000/ft1000-usb modules
cp drivers/staging/ft1000/ft1000-usb/ft1000.ko /lib/modules/3.2.0-4-686-pae/kernel/drivers/staging/
depmod
modprobe ft1000
\stoptyping

